EXTRACTED VALUE: Via Domus is fan service through and through, and does deliver one genuinely amazing moment via its ending.
There comes a time when you start to hope that the Circle of Doom in the title is actually the red ring of death so you won't have to play it anymore.
Shrek the turd, more like. [Sept 2007, p.106]
Unless you're a serious fan of boxing games seeking a fix while you wait for the next Fight Night game you may want to pass on this one.
It's not nearly as bad as the notoriously awful "Superman 64," but it's yet another chunk of kryptonite plaguing his video game career.
